  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink65-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">āṟṟāmaiyē vāyilākap pukka talaimakaṟkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink65">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>karumpunaṭu pāttiyiṟ kalitta vāmpal</l>
          <l>curumpupaci kaḷaiyum perumpuṉa lūra</l>
          <l>putalvaṉai yīṉṟaveṉ mēṉi</l>
          <l>muyaṅkaṉmō teyyaniṉ mārpucitaip patuvē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


          <l> O man from a village of great floods, where </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> a waterlily, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> flourishing in the sections planted with sugarcane, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> is enough to satisfy a bee's hunger! </l>
          <l> Do not embrace my body, </l>
          <l> that has brought forth a son. </l>
          <l> It will ruin your chest/your chest will ruin [it]. </l>


        </lg>

      </div>
    </body>
